{"type": "article", "id": 24666, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-03-30T07:00:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 16057, "name": "Norm Architects"}, {"id": 25569, "name": "One Trick Pony"}, {"id": 25570, "name": "Álvaro Díaz Hernández"}, {"id": 25571, "name": "Rom Khampanya"}, {"id": 25572, "name": "Floris Wubben"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122130iaRCSB4KnI1Ufyph.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>Frame &amp; Rest by Norm architects</h2>\n<p>丹麦设计工作室 Norm architects 在一年前推出了一个浴室系列，这是它的另一个系列，都在极简北欧风格中体现出优雅。无论是沙发、洗手池柜子还是墙上的架子都使用了纤细而方正的黑色金属做结构，搭配黑色的木材、皮垫或白色桌面，能看到包豪斯风格。在结构转折的细节处使用了黄铜来提亮，很古典。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110106jKG2myePZucQAFoD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75427873\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110106drEf2QGHqPBYKpaT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74816626\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071101062fl1ARLW6SFsCqNM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62591687\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110107blkejK193ZyrSPiX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110107X8CeGEKbQ0mdlWBS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.36185819\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Gooseneck Lazy Mount</h2>\n<p>这是一个专门放手机或平板的支架，试图让你的双手不再一直握着它，从而保持放松的姿势。设计原理和夹在桌边的台灯是一样的，它的固定方式是用螺丝旋转的，更稳定。这套支架的头还配有 5、7、10 英尺这 3 种型号的夹子以方便放多个工具。售价 48 美元，<a href=\"https://fancy.com/things/991699611141800827/Gooseneck-Lazy-Mount\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110108edvu9PQyNqMlhCKG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.91125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110108zF7slygeQcYHx9uv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110109RKonLTSUcd8EXz4N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.91166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110109RI2iHZU7lN45uqz0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110109bjyDQLxhgfEz9eRc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.485\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: Arial, STHeiti, 华文黑体, 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, Helvetica, Tahoma, 'Arial sans-serif'; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; text-align: justify; font-weight: normal;\">Classictone by Rom Khampanya</span></h2>\n<p>这三个方形的木盒子是一组音响，是用胡桃木做的，通过上面的线连接起来。胡桃木音响本身是一种怀旧，但将音响分开却是非常新鲜有趣的做法，你可以交换顺序或旋转它，就像是三个积木。带调控功能的音响可以连接电脑或其他电器，设计师来自泰国，他正在众筹这个产品，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/classictone-simple-walnut-speakers#/\">这里是众筹链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110110EMNV5X4edx7moCPU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.87222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110110XmROiNnGwQAZ5PS2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071101114UdEvPqJC6ray7GY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110111CjEdPOU4rFY9zfl0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110112bIMRdcJjk7EriXP8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Minus magazine stand by Álvaro Díaz Hernández</h2>\n<p>这是一款有线条感的杂志架，仅仅用铁棒做成。下面是一个盒子一样的空间放杂物和书籍，然后用一个较大的铁框串起，可以做手提杆或将一本看了一半的杂志扣在上面，很轻盈，也能适应多种环境。有黑白两色，白色的像是隐藏在了白色的墙壁里，也体现出了极简。售价 190 美元，<a href=\"https://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/minus-magazine-stand/\">这里是购买链接</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110112Nr6JklsRuO2p79KU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.41489362\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110113N8L2DYftKpOmJVsy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.41489362\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110113IjLwnsovAKXxplra.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.41489362\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110114S96rDCc5j7qasGU8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.41489362\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110114TFUa0qOI7f9pkVNb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.41489362\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Erosion Set by Studio Floris Wubben</h2>\n<p>这组略带皲裂和分层花纹的瓷杯来自是荷兰设计师 Floris Wubben ，他在一次意外中发现了做出这种纹理的方法，将未干燥的瓷器和瓦斯的火焰接触，而随着两者之间的距离和速度的改变也影响了温度，使瓷杯本身产生更多样的变化。这套瓷杯瓷碗都是基于此方法做出的，有些偶然和手工的痕迹。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071101151Czmxh3cW7bHBgRF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110115qZU0c3kCDWnxdm9P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110116yD3TXtB7lFzVsohu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110116cgwDuHJ1a7p3bTif.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110117i9EAmTDvMYejBPFN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Taft’s Ale House Old Wooden Tooth by One Trick Pony </h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://taftsalehouse.com\">Taft’s Ale House </a>是在美国辛辛那提（Cincinnati）成立的一家新的啤酒吧，这是他们一周年的纪念包装。 500ml 的啤酒都装在特质的木盒子里，是当地的一种传统。啤酒颈部有 9 种不一样的旗帜，其中有一款旗帜是用樱桃木片制作的，上面印出了金属色的 logo，都是细微处的简单改变，增加了节日的仪式感。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110117MY8HZIz7b9dkqxjr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.27881041\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110117oehLHrFlAPxIypD1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71933086\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110118o9gpYevNDkEsd0J8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.10037175\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071101187qcsnVM6l4pLQSdv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79182156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}